<div class="container mx-auto p-4">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-6">Events</h1>
  
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
    <!-- TODO: Move lbmf2024logo.png to Rails assets -->
    <%= image_tag 'lbmf2024logo.png', 
        class: 'w-48 h-48 md:w-72 md:h-72 mb-10 object-contain', 
        alt: 'Leaps and Bounds Music Festival 2024 Logo' %>
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl text-center space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Leaps and Bounds Music Festival</h2>
      
      <p class="text-lg font-medium">July 25-28, 2024</p>
      
      <div class="space-y-4 text-left">
        <p>
          The Leaps and Bounds Music Festival has grown from a small community 
          gathering to one of the region's premier music events. What started as 
          a single day celebration has evolved into a four-day festival showcasing 
          the incredible diversity of our local music scene.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          Our mission is to provide a platform for emerging artists while bringing 
          together established acts and music lovers from across the community. The 
          festival celebrates all genres, from indie rock and electronic music to 
          folk, jazz, and everything in between.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          This year's festival features over 100 performances across multiple venues, 
          offering something for every musical taste. From intimate acoustic sets to 
          high-energy main stage performances, the festival creates connections between 
          artists and audiences that last long after the final note is played.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          Use Live Music Locator to navigate between venues, discover new artists, 
          and plan your festival experience. Our real-time updates help you stay 
          informed about set times, venue changes, and special announcements throughout 
          the festival weekend.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="pt-4">
        <p>
          For more information and tickets, visit: 
          <%= link_to 'https://leapsandboundsfestival.com.au', 
              'https://leapsandboundsfestival.com.au', 
              target: '_blank',
              rel: 'noopener noreferrer',
              class: 'text-customBlue underline hover:text-blue-700' %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

